      <text xml:space="preserve">{{Infobox musical artist| &lt;!-- See Wikipedia:WikiProject Musicians --&gt;
| Name            = Boney M.
| Img             = Boney M 1981.jpg
| Img_capt        = Boney M in 1981
| Landscape       = 
| Background      = group_or_band
| Origin          = [[West Germany]]
| Genre           = [[Reggae music|Reggae]], [[Disco]], [[R&amp;B]]
