==Administrative divisions==
===&lt;span lang=&quot;de&quot;&gt;Regierungsbezirke&lt;/span&gt; (administrative districts)===
[[File:Bavarian Admin Districts.jpg|thumb|Administrative Districts of Bavaria]]

Bavaria is divided into 7 administrative districts called &lt;span lang=&quot;de&quot;&gt;''Regierungsbezirke''&lt;/span&gt; (singular &lt;span lang=&quot;de&quot;&gt;''Regierungsbezirk''&lt;/span&gt;).

# [[Upper Franconia]] ({{lang-de|Oberfranken}})
# [[Middle Franconia]] ({{lang|de|''Mittelfranken''}})
# [[Lower Franconia]] ({{lang|de|''Unterfranken''}})
# [[Swabia (administrative region)|Swabia]] ({{lang|de|''Schwaben''}})
# [[Upper Palatinate]] ({{lang|de|''Oberpfalz''}})
# [[Upper Bavaria]] ({{lang|de|''Oberbayern''}})
# [[Lower Bavaria]] ({{lang|de|''Niederbayern''}})

