*[[Karolina Gočeva]], singer
*[[Hristijan Spirovski]], pianist
*[[Janko Konstantinov]], architect

==Twin towns — sister cities==
[[Image:Hotel Epinal in Bitola.JPG|right|thumb|200px|Hotel &quot;Epinal&quot; in the center of Bitola, named in honor of the [[France|French]] city [[Épinal]], a twin town of Bitola. In return, a quarter in the city of Épinal is called Bitola, and a [[Flag of the Republic of Macedonia|Macedonian flag]] is flown there.]]
Bitola participates in [[town twinning]] to foster good international relations. Its current partners include:
