* {{flagicon|Turkey}} [[Bursa]], [[Turkey]]
* {{flagicon|Slovenia}} [[Kranj]], [[Slovenia]]
* {{flagicon|Australia}} [[Rockdale, New South Wales|Rockdale]], [[Australia]]
* {{flagicon|Ukraine}} [[Kremenchuk]], [[Ukraine]]
* {{flagicon|Bulgaria}} [[Pleven]], [[Bulgaria]]
* {{flagicon|Germany}} [[Kaiserslautern]], [[Germany]]
* {{flagicon|Montenegro}} [[Herceg Novi]], [[Montenegro]]
* {{flagicon|Sweden}} [[Trelleborg]], [[Sweden]]
* {{flagicon|Serbia}} [[Stari Grad, Belgrade]], [[Serbia]]
* {{flagicon|Serbia}} [[Požarevac]], [[Serbia]]
* {{flagicon|Greece}} [[Edessa]], [[Greece]]
* {{flagicon|Greece}} [[Kozani]], [[Greece]]
* {{flagicon|Albania}} [[Korçë]], [[Albania]]
