&lt;references group=T /&gt;

==New Testament==
{{See also|Development of the New Testament canon|Template:Books of the New Testament}}
In general, among [[Christian denominations]], the ''New Testament Canon'' is an agreed-upon list of 27 books, although book order can vary. The book order is the same in the Greek Orthodox, Catholic, and Protestant tradition.&lt;ref group=N name=Luther/&gt; The [[Slavonic Orthodox|Slavonic]], Armenian and Ethiopian traditions have different New Testament book orders to this.

